  "module": {
    "path": "src/common/logging",
    "name": "logging",
    "purpose": "Common database telemetry logging module. tag.rs defines the serializable LogTag severity enum (Info, Warning, Error, Debug); message.rs defines the serializable LogMessage record carrying a tag, message text, and emit/arrival millisecond timestamps with tagged constructors and a crate-visible arrival stamp; error.rs defines the LoggingError enum with config, I/O, database, serialization, already-configured, and not-hosting variants; logger.rs owns the Logger telemetry client that either hosts a TCP telemetry server persisting messages to a local redb database or connects to a remote server, streaming length-prefixed JSON LogMessage frames.",
